messages.content: Thanks Andy! Good luck with your year abroad. I'm sure it will be awesome. I hope I get to see you sometime when you get back :)
Awesome! One more semester isn't too bad. And Chicago would be pretty cool. Good luck finishing up

That is really cool. I just googled the islands and you are basically going to be living on a beach for a year huh? Have fun! I still have a semester left of school and then next summer I'll be starting my internship either here at state or in Chicago.
I'm going to the Marshall Islands to teach, probably English. It's one of those teach abroad programs
Wow! Yea I wish I could have seen you too. I'm glad I was able to talk to you today before you go. Where are you going & why?

I just know the bare essentials. I can't "tag" a "status wall," or anything complex like that. I'm actually using a facebook because I'm leaving the country tomorrow, and I'm going to use this and a blog to stay connected a little bit. I wish I would have met up with you at least once this summer before I left; I'll be leaving for a year. I guess we'll just have a lot to talk about next time we run into each other. Hope you're doing well.
WHAT! NO WAY! I can't believe you have a Facebook now. do you even know how to use it?! Haha :P
